Description: The top class WRC before 17, following 2011-2016 regulation. This is a tribute to this class based on Rally2, using Rally2's body kits, BRC's chassis and suspension, and a two layer wing within the projection of the car. Equipped with a special 33mm turbo restrictor, 6-speed sequential paddle shifter and 50/50 clutched transfercase. Tarmac spec has about 200mm of suspension travel and 355mm brake discs.
